' 	- important entities to consider: goods (items, products), racks where the food
' and drinks are available to pick, warehouse (central, local), price list, orders, invoices, categories of goods, transport from the central warehouse to a local branch (store)
' 	- required: create an UML class diagram that captures relevant entities and relationships between them
